<p>Honestly, driving along, and exploring, this part of Oahu was one of the highlights of our trip!</p>
<h2>Kahana Bay Beach</h2>
<p>The Kahana Bay Beach is a secluded and relatively calm beach for the North Shore. From the number of pyres on the beach, I got a sense that this beach sees a lot of bonfires.</p>
<div id="attachment_6926" style="width: 1210px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://droneandslr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/north-shore-oahu-hawaii-16.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-6926" class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-6926 size-full" src="//droneandslr.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://droneandslr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/north-shore-oahu-hawaii-16.jpg" alt="Kahana Bay Beach Park, North Shore, Oahu" width="1200" height="675" /><noscript><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-6926" class="wp-image-6926 size-full" src="https://droneandslr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/north-shore-oahu-hawaii-16.jpg" alt="Kahana Bay Beach Park, North Shore, Oahu" width="1200" height="675" /></noscript></a><p id="caption-attachment-6926" class="wp-caption-text">Kahana Bay Beach Park, North Shore, Oahu</p></div>
<h2>Punalu&#8217;u Beach</h2>
<p>Not to be confused with the <a href="https://droneandslr.com/travel-blog/hawaii/punaluu-black-sand-beach-big-island/">Punaluu Black Sand Beach on the Big Island</a>, the Punaluu Beach on Oahu is thin, narrow stretch of sand located along the North Shore. The views of the sea, and the views of the mountains behind made this beach unique in my opinion.</p>
<div id="attachment_6417" style="width: 1210px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://droneandslr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/north-shore-oahu-aerial-photo-24.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-6417" class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-6417 size-full" src="//droneandslr.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://droneandslr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/north-shore-oahu-aerial-photo-24.jpg" alt="Punalu'u Beach on the North Shore, Oahu" width="1200" height="750" /><noscript><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-6417" class="wp-image-6417 size-full" src="https://droneandslr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/north-shore-oahu-aerial-photo-24.jpg" alt="Punalu'u Beach on the North Shore, Oahu" width="1200" height="750" /></noscript></a><p id="caption-attachment-6417" class="wp-caption-text">Punalu&#8217;u Beach on the North Shore, Oahu</p></div>
<h2>Turtle Bay</h2>
<p><a href="https://www.booking.com/hotel/us/turtle-bay-resort.html?aid=1339046&amp;no_rooms=1&amp;group_adults=2&amp;room1=A%2CA" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Turtle Bay Resort</a> is probably the most iconic, and biggest resort (850 acres) on Oahu. Although not as famous as Kualoa Ranch, Turtle Bay Resort has also been featured in numerous Hollywood movies from <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0800039/">Forgetting Sarah Marshall</a>, to <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2823054/">Mike and Dave Need Wedding Dates</a>. So, naturally we had to stay here.</p>
<p>The resort&#8217;s beaches and snorkeling areas aren&#8217;t restricted to the general public. So, even if you aren&#8217;t staying at Turtle Bay Resort, head on down to the Kuilima Cave for snorkeling, or to Turtle Bay to see magnificent sea turtles.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.booking.com/hotel/us/turtle-bay-resort.html?aid=1339046&amp;no_rooms=1&amp;group_adults=2&amp;room1=A%2CA" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">But just for good measure, I&#8217;d highly recommend staying at this iconic property in Hawaii</a> (even if it&#8217;s just for a night)!</p>
<div id="attachment_6888" style="width: 1210px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://droneandslr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/turtle-bay-resort-oahu-hawaii-59.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-6888" class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-6888 size-full" src="//droneandslr.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://droneandslr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/turtle-bay-resort-oahu-hawaii-59.jpg" alt="The view from our room at Turtle Bay Resort, North Shore, Oahu" width="1200" height="460" /><noscript><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-6888" class="wp-image-6888 size-full" src="https://droneandslr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/turtle-bay-resort-oahu-hawaii-59.jpg" alt="The view from our room at Turtle Bay Resort, North Shore, Oahu" width="1200" height="460" /></noscript></a><p id="caption-attachment-6888" class="wp-caption-text">The view from our room at Turtle Bay Resort, North Shore, Oahu</p></div>
<h2>Banzai Pipeline</h2>
<p>Banzai Pipeline (also known as &#8220;Pipeline&#8221; or just &#8220;Pipe&#8221;) is another epic beach worth visiting. The beach is famous for its notorious waves that draw surfers from all across the island.</p>

