<h2>Shark&#8217;s Cove</h2>
<p>Shark&#8217;s Cove is famous for two things &#8211; snorkeling, and <a href="https://droneandslr.com/travel-blog/hawaii/north-shore-oahu-food/">food trucks</a>.</p>
<div style="clear:both; margin-top:0em; margin-bottom:1em;"><a href="https://droneandslr.com/travel-blog/hawaii/north-shore-oahu-food/" target="_self" class="u8aba09dd46c3d2f723bf756870aa233f"><style> .u8aba09dd46c3d2f723bf756870aa233f { padding:0px; margin: 0; padding-top:1em!important; padding-bottom:1em!important; width:100%; display: block; font-weight:bold; background-color:inherit; border:0!important; border-left:4px solid #F1C40F!important; text-decoration:none; } .u8aba09dd46c3d2f723bf756870aa233f:active, .u8aba09dd46c3d2f723bf756870aa233f:hover { opacity: 1; transition: opacity 250ms; webkit-transition: opacity 250ms; text-decoration:none; } .u8aba09dd46c3d2f723bf756870aa233f { transition: background-color 250ms; webkit-transition: background-color 250ms; opacity: 1; transition: opacity 250ms; webkit-transition: opacity 250ms; } .u8aba09dd46c3d2f723bf756870aa233f .ctaText { font-weight:bold; color:#2C3E50; text-decoration:none; font-size: 16px; } .u8aba09dd46c3d2f723bf756870aa233f .postTitle { color:#2980B9; text-decoration: underline!important; font-size: 16px; } .u8aba09dd46c3d2f723bf756870aa233f:hover .postTitle { text-decoration: underline!important; } </style><div style="padding-left:1em; padding-right:1em;"><span class="ctaText">You might also like</span>&nbsp; <span class="postTitle">North Shore, Oahu - A Food Lover's Paradise</span></div></a></div>
<p>The rocks in the area provide a natural bay for fish, and sea turtles to stay within, and feed. That&#8217;s what makes it a perfect spot for snorkeling. It&#8217;s also not as crowded as Hanauma Bay.</p>
<div id="attachment_6404" style="width: 1210px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://droneandslr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/north-shore-oahu-aerial-photo-10.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-6404" class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-6404 size-full" src="//droneandslr.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://droneandslr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/north-shore-oahu-aerial-photo-10.jpg" alt="Shark's Cove, Oahu North Shore" width="1200" height="833" /><noscript><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-6404" class="wp-image-6404 size-full" src="https://droneandslr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/north-shore-oahu-aerial-photo-10.jpg" alt="Shark's Cove, Oahu North Shore" width="1200" height="833" /></noscript></a><p id="caption-attachment-6404" class="wp-caption-text">Shark&#8217;s Cove, Oahu North Shore</p></div>
<h2>Waimea Bay Beach Park</h2>
<p>Waimea Bay Beach was another one of my favourite beaches on the North Shore. The beach has a giant diving cliff from which divers jump into the ocean, which gives it a unique character.</p>
<p>Also, it&#8217;s probably the only beach that I&#8217;ve been to that <a href="https://droneandslr.com/drone-aerial-photography/hawaii/">needs air traffic control for drones</a>!</p>

