<h2>Laniakea Beach &#8211; Famous For Sea Turtles (Honu)</h2>
<p>Although Laniakea Beach stretches for miles, you&#8217;ll always find most of the crowd concentrated in one corner of the beach. The reason &#8211; <strong>sea turtles</strong>.</p>

		<style type='text/css'>
			#gallery-13 {
				margin: auto;
